snippet.title: 💫Gameplay footage with UI💫
snippet.description:
The newest gameplay footage with UI has just been revealed‼
This edition is from the exactly same beta version which showed at '2022 Korea Blockchain Week'. 
Not only the action, characters and Frontier Town, but you can also see the "Stella Strike", which is a powerful skill through the combination of characters in your party!🤩

Join our Community to learn more 👇
